intro: A puzzle game featuring many adorable maid girls has arrived!
description:
Collect the pieces of cute maid girls and complete the puzzles!

There are 15 stages in total.
As you clear each stage, the difficulty increases!

Stages 1–10: 30 pieces
Stages 11–15: 50 pieces

The final stage is a challenging one with no background watermark!
Take your time, examine each piece closely, and complete the puzzle!

When you complete a puzzle, high-resolution maid girls will be added to your gallery♪

=====================
At “AGE,” we support video creators who stream or record gameplay.
No permission is required for game commentary or streaming.
